Through use of this website, we aspire to elicit an emotional response of empathy and affect positive change throughout the globe via contributions to charitable and political organizations.

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Players
-Target User
  Identifies as female
  Has interest in global issues which affect women
  Has a desire to contribute positively to women all over the globe
  Has internet access via web browser
  Has no age restriction

-User Profile
  Consists of the original demographic information entered by user
  Includes data statistics associated with demographic information
  
-Parallel Profile
  Originates as a copy of the user profile
  User can continually update one demographic point at a time to create the modified parallel profile
  Includes data statistics continually updated as demographic information is updated
  
-Comparison Profile
  Pre-configured profile used to compare with a user profile
  Representative of a particular geographic location or women's issue
  Includes data statistics associated with demographic information

-Organization
  Qualified political or charitable organization centered around women's issue(s)
  Includes verified contact information
  Includes verified method(s) or suggestions for contributing

-Account
  Secure
  Always includes one current, complete, unique User Profile
  Saves any number of additional parallel profiles associated with a single user
  Saves favorite organizations and associated comparison profile(s), if any

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Stories
-Website Navigation
  As a user, I want to scroll from first to second page
  Upon form submission, current page should swipe either to the right or bottom to display the new page
  Upon trigger of a click event, current page should swipe either to the right or bottom to display the new page

-Profile
  As a user, I want to be able to enter a minimum of demographic information during profile creation
  As a user, I want to be able to enter optional demographic information during profile creation
  As a user, I want to be directed my summary profile page after initial submission

-Side by Side Comparison
  As a user, I want to be able to compare my profile directly to one of many pre-built profiles via a side by side comparison
  From the side by side comparison, I want to be able to continue choosing from available pre-built profiles to engage in additional side by side comparisons
  As a user, I want to be able to return to my summary profile page or access the story building page with my user profile demographic information

-Story Building
  As a user, I want to be able to change one or multiple categories of my user profile to create and view a new parallel profile without modification to my user profile
  As a user, I want to be able to continue modifying and viewing my parallel profile demographic information without modification to my user profile
  As a user, I want to be able to return to my summary profile page or access the side by side comparison page with my user profile demographic information

-Giving
  As a user, I want to have direct access to a page listing multiple charitable and/or political organizations
  As a user, I want to be directed to organizations which are specific to the side by side or story building comparison I built
  As a user, I want to be able to search for relevant organizations by name, type, or focus
  As a user, I want organization search results to provide me with all pertinent contact information or links to act on donating to organization, contacting organization, or participating in organization activities
  As a user, I want to be able to return to my summary profile page, access the side by side comparison page or story building page with my user profile demographic information

-Accounts
  As a user, I want to have an option to create an account associated with my user profile
  As a user, I want to be able to access my secure account using a unique and secure username/password combination
  As a user, I want to be able to access my summary profile page from my account
  As a user, I want to be able to update my demographic information from my account
  As a user, I want to  be able to save multiple parallel "what if" profiles to my account
  As a user, I want to be able to indicate and save my favorite organization(s) to my account

-Future Features
  As a user, I want to access this app on a mobile device
  If a user attempts to navigate back in the website, page(s) should swipe in the opposite direction of previous page(s) navigation
  As a user, I want my payment information securely stored for future donations
  As a user, I want access to news related to my favorite organizations, women's issue, or geographical locations
